Cape Town’s V&A Waterfront to Get $74 Million Revamp, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-06-10T05:09:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/cape-town-s-v-a-waterfront-to-get-74-million-revamp-business-day-reports.html
Growthpoint Properties Ltd. (GRT)  and the
Public Investment Corp. will invest 500 million rand ($74
million) upgrading  Cape Town ’s Victoria & Alfred Waterfront,
Business Day reported, citing Growthpoint Chief Executive
Officer Norbert Sasse.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
